    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Stagecraft powder was first created in the Veskarium for use during elaborate ceremonies and thematic productions to memorialize great heroes and their conquests. This single-use powder enchants its target with an attention-grabbing aura. As a move action, you can dust yourself or an adjacent willing ally with stagecraft powder, granting the target a +4 circumstance bonus to Bluff checks to create a diversion, to Charisma-based Profession checks to earn a living, and to Sleight of Hand checks to entertain. The dust also imposes a –4 penalty to Stealth checks. Stagecraft powder’s effects wear off in 1 hour.</p>\n<p><em>(Equip to activate)</em></p>"
    },
